examples.text: Bir kadın çizeceksin / Onun gibi bırakıp gitmeyecek
examples.translation: You will draw a woman / She won't leave you like the last one

glosses: to cross out, strike out, scratch out, cancel

etymology: Inherited from Ottoman Turkish چیزمك (çizmek, “to draw, sketch”). Cognate of Old Uyghur [script needed] (çız-, “to draw”), Azerbaijani cızmaq, Bashkir һыҙыу (hıźıw, “to draw”), Chuvash чӗрме (čĕrme, “to tear, scratch, draw”), Kyrgyz сызуу (sızuu, “to draw”), Turkmen çyzmak (“to draw, sketch, design”), Uyghur سىزماق (sizmaq, “to draw”), Uzbek chizmoq (“to draw, paint”) etc.
